# Pokemon TCG Layout — Component-by-Component Changes

## Navigation (.nav, NavBar.tsx)
**Current**: White bg `rgba(255,255,255,0.82)` with red bottom shadow
**Target**: Dark navy bg with subtle blue glow

```css
.nav {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.92);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(60,90,166,0.25), 0 12px 40px -24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}
.navlink { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
.navlink:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: #fff; }
.navlink.active { background: #FFCB05; color: #0a0a0c; }
.brand { color: #fff; }
.brand-chain { color: #FFCB05; }
```

## Hero Section (.hero-xl, page.tsx)
**Current**: White bg with dot pattern
**Target**: Dark gradient with vibrant elements

```css
.hero-xl {
  background:
    radial-gradient(120% 120% at 88% -10%, rgba(60,90,166,0.2), transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(120% 120% at -8% 110%, rgba(227,53,13,0.15), transparent 55%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #0F172A 0%, #1A1A2E 100%);
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}
.display { color: #FFFFFF; }
.lede { color: #B0B0C0; }
.chain-tag { background: #FFCB05; color: #0a0a0c; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
.btn.accent { background: #FFCB05; color: #0a0a0c; }
.hstat b { color: #FFFFFF; }
.hstat span { color: #8A8FB0; }
```

## Feature Cards (.feature)
**Current**: White glassmorphism
**Target**: Dark glassmorphism

```css
.feature {
  background: rgba(22,34,68,0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}
.feature:hover {
  border-color: rgba(255,203,5,0.2);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -28px rgba(255,203,5,0.15);
}
.feature h3 { color: #FFFFFF; }
.feature p { color: #8A8FB0; }
```

## Marquee (.marquee)
**Current**: Red background
**Target**: Keep red OR switch to Pokemon Yellow — either works with dark theme
```css
.marquee { background: #FFCB05; }
.marquee-item { color: #0a0a0c; }
```

## PC Band (.pc-band)
**Current**: Pink/white gradient
**Target**: Dark with subtle blue gradient
```css
.pc-band {
  background: radial-gradient(120% 160% at 100% 0%, #1E2D4A, #16213E 60%);
  color: #FFFFFF;
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}
```

## CTA Band (.cta-band)
**Current**: White-ish with red radial
**Target**: Dark with yellow glow
```css
.cta-band {
  background: radial-gradient(120% 120% at 50% 0%, rgba(255,203,5,0.15), transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #0F172A, #1A1A2E);
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  color: #FFFFFF;
}
```

## Buttons
```css
.btn { background: #FFCB05; color: #0a0a0c; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
.btn.secondary { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #fff; }
.btn.ghost { color: #fff; }
.btn.ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
.btn.gold { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFCB05, #E6B800); color: #0a0a0c; }
.btn.glow { animation-name: ctaGlowYellow; }
/* Add new keyframe: */
@keyframes ctaGlowYellow {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: var(--sh); }
  50% { box-shadow: var(--sh), 0 0 24px 3px rgba(255,203,5,0.5); }
}
```

## Login Page
- `.login-card-premium` — dark bg with glow border
- `.login-step` — dark panels
- `.login-hero-panel` — dark, text white
- Wallet adapter buttons already reference `--accent`, so they'll auto-update

